  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps 10 Guests</strong></p>
<p>Chalet Bouton d'Or offers easy access to the skiing with just a 2 minute walk to the piste. The chalet is light and airy with a separate dining room and comfortable lounge area with large south-facing balcony and views of the pistes. <strong>New for this winter a hot tub has been installed on the terrace</strong>.</p>
<p>The blue Petite Aiguille piste is close by and you ski down here for the Petite Aiguille chairlift back up to the glacier side or the Côte chairlift for the Vallée Blanche side of the valley. Otherwise the <strong>free</strong> resort shuttle bus stops just outside and it runs every 15 minutes during the day. The comfortable bedrooms all have en suite facilties (the shower rooms in rooms 2-5 are newly renovated) and hairdryers to share. The chalet offers stylish and comfortable accommodation which has been recently refurbished and with the Inghams catered service provides all the ingredients for a successful ski holiday to Les 2 Alpes.</p>]]></description>
